"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-07-28-simone-biles-suffers-injury-scare-olympics-return-paris-21312718\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Simone Biles suffered what appeared to be a minor injury scare during her triumphant return toOlympicsaction inParis.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 117, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The American turned in superb displays in the artistic gymnastics qualification events on Sunday morning, topping the leader boards to markher returnin style.\", \"from\": 119, \"to\": 277, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 123, \"end\": 131, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999752719369722, \"rank\": 1.142587688998169e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She completed all four routines to get Team USA off to an excellent start but there was a brief moment of concern for the 27-year-old following her first event.\", \"from\": 279, \"to\": 439, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 318, \"end\": 326, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.999429244344571, \"rank\": 0.00031649626534316187, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles briefly exited the competition floor inside Bercy Arena with what appeared to be an ankle injury.\", \"from\": 441, \"to\": 544, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 491, \"end\": 502, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Accor_Arena\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bercy Arena\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Accor_Arena\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Accor_Arena\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She appeared to notice the injury after a warm-up routine ahead of her floor event.\", \"from\": 545, \"to\": 628, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro.co.uk's live blog for latest news on the Paris Olympics  'As soon as I took off, I felt it,' Biles was heard saying to Team USA doctor Dr Marcia Faustin, 'It's right there on my calf.\", \"from\": 630, \"to\": 826, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 762, \"end\": 770, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.999429244344571, \"rank\": 0.00031649626534316187, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 781, \"end\": 787, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marcia_Overstrand\", \"score\": 0.999955057141245, \"rank\": 4.417447404198139e-05, \"text\": \"Marcia\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marcia_Overstrand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marcia_Overstrand\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Right where I had that tear.'\", \"from\": 827, \"to\": 856, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles still scored a huge 14.600 in the floor event but was seen grimacing on some of her landings during her routine.\", \"from\": 858, \"to\": 976, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She re-emerged for her first vault event wearing heavy strapping on her left foot.\", \"from\": 978, \"to\": 1060, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But it did not prevent her from making more Olympic history moments later, becoming the first woman to land the Yurchenko double pike in an Olympic event, scoring a massive 15.800.\", \"from\": 1062, \"to\": 1242, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1174, \"end\": 1183, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yurchenko_(vault)\", \"score\": 0.9924615128801457, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yurchenko\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yurchenko_(vault)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yurchenko_(vault)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles finished her morning on the bars, smiling and saluting the crowd as she left the floor.\", \"from\": 1244, \"to\": 1337, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a dazzling display from one of the greatest athletes in Olympic history, whose Tokyo 2020 Gameswas derailed by a bout of the 'twisties'.\", \"from\": 1339, \"to\": 1482, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1425, \"end\": 1430, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999377288955851, \"rank\": 5.4622328387861805e-05, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles was forced to withdraw from several events and ultimately ended up taking a two-year hiatus from the sport she once dominated.\", \"from\": 1484, \"to\": 1616, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But her impressive return on Day Two of action in the French capital suggests she is back to her best.\", \"from\": 1618, \"to\": 1720, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1672, \"end\": 1678, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9863594560349592, \"rank\": 0.010290241363660397, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Shane Lowry can upset the odds by winning Olympic gold for Ireland  ArrowMORE:Olympics organisers apologise after another 'disrespectful' mistake angers fans  ArrowMORE:Olympics star pulls out of Paris event because she caught a cold  Your guide to the week in football.\", \"from\": 1722, \"to\": 2002, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1791, \"end\": 1798, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9322384691097765, \"rank\": 0.05157613665922803, \"text\": \"Ireland\"